Bring your unwanted or broken electronics to the annual Klahanie Recycle event this

Saturday, May 25th from 10am-2pm at the Lakeside Pool parking lot!

See list below of accepted and not-accepted items.

Accepted: TVs (any) Computer Monitor PC/Tower Laptop/Tablet Cell Phones Ink /Cartridge Motherboards Servers Network Switches Circuit boards/Misc. boards Landline Phones Stereo/Receivers DVD/VCR Toner/Cartridge Microwaves VHS Tapes/CDs/DVDs Mixed Boxes: wire/cable etc. UPS System - UPS Battery

Not Accepted: Any Hazardous Waste Printers (desktop) Copiers LED ACID Batteries Batteries (Alkaline / Li-ion NiMH NiCad etc.) Fluorescent Tubes CFL Bulbs

Please remove any batteries that might be in items such as remote controls etc. prior to recycling them!

-Klahanie HOA
